"""
This file is a reference for the various components that we use in the site
"""

===========
Website Components
===========

===========
Javascript Objects
===========

Post:

title = Title of the post. Shown in PostSnippet and Post
date = Last modified time.
type = Value of post (String: "Text", "Image", "Link")
extract = textarea value
post_id = unique post identifier
author_id = ID of poster
group = group name
image_path = location of (optional image)
comments = List of comments for post

Comment:

author_id = id of commenter
post_id = id of corresponding post
content = text of comment/url of image
content_type = type of content, image/text
date = date comment posted
